### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/local-login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "emadunan@gmail.com",
  "password": "emadunan"
}

### reset password
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/users/me/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "emademad",
  "newPassword": "emadunan"
}

### Update bookmark
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/users/bookmark
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "verseId": 170,
  "profileEmail": "emadunan@gmail.com"
}

### Toggle user theme
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/users/me/theme HTTP/1.1

### Change user ui language
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/users/me/lang HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uiLang": "ar"
}

### Get logged in user (decode user)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/me

### Get all bookmark for user
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/bookmark

### Delete Account Permanently
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/users/profile
